title: Buying Policy, Per Cent Reporting Commitments 90 Days or Longer for the United States
notes:
From January 1950 To April 1955, Per Cents Show All Purchases (Production, M.R.O. And Capital Expenditures). From May 1955 On, Per Cents Show Production Materials Only. Source: National Association Of Purchasing Agents, H. Stern'S Files.
